	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hey all Druids - <br>I am a Level 36 Halfing Druid. I am needing some advice on armor for me. I have seen the post about the &quot;Brain of the Beaked Bear&quot; I am going to go try for it, but I have three slots open right now &amp; I need help finding out what I can get at my level &amp; where I could hunt it. I like to solo kill, but I can get a group together for some kills. Here you can see my armor - <br><br>Primary Melee: Velium Stone Mace<br>DMG:7 DL:22 STR:+3 WIS:+3<br>Secondary Melee: Sarnak Battle Shield<br>AC:+25 STR: +5 STA:+5 MR:+10<br> FR:+10 CR:+10 HP:+40<br>Ranged Weapon: Preserved Split Paw Eye<br>FR:+2<br>Ear: A Saprohyte Eye<br>AC:+2 CHA:+5 HP:+20 Mana:+20<br>Ear: Earring of Fire Reflection<br>AC:+1 FR:+2<br>Neck: Aviak Charm<br>DEX:+2 WIS:+1 PR:+1<br>Face: Stained Cloth Mask<br>AC:+6 CHA:+4 PR:+5 DR:+5 HP:+20 Mana:+20<br>Head: Cat Skull Cap<br>AC:+4 MR:+2<br>Shoulders: Lizardscale Mantle<br>AC:+5 WIS:+3 INT:+3<br>Finger: Silver Rose Engagement Ring<br>INT:+2 (I have no clue why I have this!)<br>Finger: Jaded Platinum Ring<br>AC:+4 HP:+20 Mana:+20<br>Wrist: Bracelet of Woven Grass<br>AC:+1 INT:+3 HP:+12 Effect: Spell Haste I<br>Wrist: Golden Jaded Bracelet<br>AC:+2 HP:+15 Mana:+15<br>Arms: Empty<br>Chest: Brwon Chitin Protector<br>AC:+12 STA:+9 AGI:+9 DEX:+9<br>Back: Cloak of the Ice Bear<br>AC:+8 CR:+20 HP:+10<br>Feet: Golden Efreeti Boots<br>AC:+5 WIS:+9 INT:+9<br>Legs: Empty<br>Waist: Split Paw Hide Belt<br>AC+5 PR:+5<br>Hands: Empty<br><br>Well, fellow Druids that is my armor. If you could help me out with my empty slots &amp; maybe a few of the other slots too. Also I play on Rallos Zek look me up some time too. <br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Thu Jul 11 11:02:39 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Nawsonbones 13 Troll Shadow Knight<br>Helian (Balance of Justice) 36 Halfing Druid<br></td></tr>
